Day 37: Copy File to Docker Container

Date: October 4, 2025
Overview
Learned to transfer files between host and containers.
Key Concepts Learned

Docker cp command
Container filesystem
File permissions in containers
Bidirectional copying

Commands Used
bashdocker cp /local/file container_name:/path/in/container
docker cp container_name:/path/in/container /local/path
Challenges Faced
File ownership and permissions can change during copy. Had to understand container user contexts.
